To add Prometheus (for metrics collection) and Grafana (for visualization) to your FastAPI app, you need to:
1 Instrument your FastAPI application to expose metrics in a format Prometheus can scrape.
2 Run Prometheus configured to scrape your app’s /metrics endpoint.
3 Run Grafana connected to Prometheus as a data source, then build or import dashboards.



taskkill /F /IM "Docker Desktop.exe" 2>$null
taskkill /F /IM "com.docker.backend.exe" 2>$null
